## Section Structure (Theme-Based)

### Preferred Structure
```
**[System] assay flow**
  - Platform overview and working principle
    ↓
**Assay characterization**
  - Optimization results (combined)
  - Analytical performance (LOD, dynamic range)
    ↓
**[System] performance for [target] detection**
  - Validation experiments
  - Gold standard comparison
    ↓
**[System] for [application]**
  - Clinical performance
```

### Anti-Pattern: Over-Fragmented (AVOID)
```
❌ Signal template optimization
❌ Time-resolved signal kinetics  
❌ Reproducibility assessment
❌ Sensitivity for protein detection
❌ Specificity for protein detection
...etc (15+ sections)
```

