### 1. Sentence Starter Diversification (CRITICAL)

**Target**: Maximum {{ (results.we_usage.mean * 100) | round }}% of sentences start with "We"

| "We" Sentence | Result-Centric Alternative |
|---------------|---------------------------|
| "We validated the probe..." | "The analytical signal (∆r) was maximal when..." |
| "We observed that..." | "[Observation] was observed in..." |
| "We determined the LOD..." | "The limit of detection was established at..." |
| "We developed..." | "[System] was built upon..." |
| "We compared..." | "In comparison with [method], [system] demonstrated..." |

