```

### 3. Figure Reference Patterns

| Pattern | Usage |
|---------|-------|
| `"(**Fig. 1a**)"` | Parenthetical (preferred) |
| `"(**Fig. 3a,b**)"` | Grouped panels |
| `"(**Supplementary Fig. 1**)"` | Supplementary references |

### 4. Quantitative Expressions

- Limit of detection: `"LOD of 10 pM"`
- Dynamic range: `"spanning 4 orders of magnitude"`
- Fold changes: `"~70-fold enhancement"`
